      <hedline>
        <hl1>Introduction</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Reader response to August 20 cover article on piracy at sea and Gov Gary Johnson's campaign for partial drug legalization (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Our cover article on piracy prompted mail asserting that capitalism is not to blame for the resurgence but is merely another victim. Readers said yes to Gov. Gary Johnson's campaign for partial drug legalization but no to his ''bootstrap'' approach to poverty. And Stephen King has second thoughts.</p>
      </block>
